1. *Košta* mi je dosta novca da kupim novi automobil. (It cost me a lot of money to buy a new car.)

2. Ne znam koliko će me *koštati* da platim račun. (I don't know how much it will cost me to pay the bill.)

3. *Koštao* je mnogo truda da napravim ovo. (It cost a lot of effort to make this.)

4. *Koštaće* li nas puno novca da odemo na put? (Will it cost us a lot of money to go on a trip?)

5. Ne mogu da verujem koliko mi je *koštala* ta odluka. (I can't believe how much that decision cost me.)